  <brief_title>Mind-Body Skills Groups for the Treatment of War-Related Trauma in Children in Gaza</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Study of Mind-Body Skills Groups for the Treatment of War-Related Trauma in Children in Gaza</official_title>
