  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to determine whether participation in a mind-body skills
      program by war-traumatized children in Gaza will result in improvement of posttraumatic
      stress symptoms, depression, and decreased hopelessness compared to a control group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
