  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  having experienced a political violence or war-related criterion A stressor

          -  meeting the American Psychiatric Association (DSM-IV-TR) criteria for PTSD according
             to screening scores on the Child PTSD Symptom Scale

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  former psychosocial or medical treatment for mental health conditions

          -  significant cognitive impairment
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
